            <p>An Student is a company that provides air transport services for traveling passengers and freight. Student utilize aircraft to supply these services and may form partnerships or alliances with other student for codeshare agreements. Generally, Student companies are recognized with an air operating certificate or license issued by a governmental aviation body.</p>
